{"id": "figure_018", "modality": "figures", "name": "U-Net segmentation (vanilla)", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG reproducing the classic U-Net segmentation architecture. Title 'U-Net (Ronneberger et al., 2015)'. A symmetric U: contracting path of 5 levels of double-conv blocks descending (channels 64,128,256,512,1024) with 2x2 max-pool down-arrows; expanding path of 4 levels ascending (512,256,128,64) with up-conv arrows; horizontal dashed copy-and-crop skip connections linking each encoder level to the SAME-height decoder level; a final 1x1 conv to the output segmentation map. Each feature-map block is labeled with its channel count; resolution annotations on the left.", "requirements": ["A symmetric U-shape with a 5-level contracting path and a 4-level expanding path", "Each feature-map block is labeled with its channel count (64,128,256,512,1024 down; 512,256,128,64 up)", "Each of the four copy-and-crop skip connections is horizontal and links encoder and decoder levels at the SAME height", "Down-arrows are labeled 'max pool 2x2' and up-arrows 'up-conv 2x2'", "A final 1x1 conv connects to an output segmentation map block", "The contracting and expanding arms are vertically symmetric (corresponding levels share a top edge)", "No feature-map block overlaps another; no skip arrow passes through a block label", "Sibling blocks at the same level are equal-size and aligned", "The whole figure fits in 1920x1080 with no scrollbar", "A legend maps colors/arrow styles; resolution annotations present; nothing clipped or misaligned"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4978, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 4644}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4879, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 5449}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4350, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 4718}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_018_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_018_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>U-Net Architecture</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        \n        h1 {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin: 0 0 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>U-Net (Ronneberger et al., 2015)</h1>\n        \n        <svg width=\"1840\" height=\"900\" viewBox=\"0 0 1840 900\">\n            <!-- Background -->\n            <rect width=\"1840\" height=\"900\" fill=\"none\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Resolution labels on the left -->\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"150\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\" text-anchor=\"middle\">572\u00d7572</text>\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"250\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\" text-anchor=\"middle\">284\u00d7284</text>\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"350\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\" text-anchor=\"middle\">142\u00d7142</text>\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"450\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\" text-anchor=\"middle\">71\u00d771</text>\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"550\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\" text-anchor=\"middle\">35\u00d735</text>\n            \n            <!-- Input -->\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"120\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"140\" y=\"145\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Input</text>\n            <text x=\"140\" y=\"165\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Image</text>\n            \n            <!-- Contracting Path (Encoder) -->\n            <!-- Level 1 -->\n            <rect x=\"240\" y=\"120\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"290\" y=\"145\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"290\" y=\"165\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">64</text>\n            \n            <!-- Down arrow 1 -->\n            <path d=\"M 290 200 L 290 220\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"215\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">2\u00d72 max pool</text>\n            \n            <!-- Level 2 -->\n            <rect x=\"240\" y=\"220\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"290\" y=\"245\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"290\" y=\"265\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">128</text>\n            \n            <!-- Down arrow 2 -->\n            <path d=\"M 290 300 L 290 320\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Level 3 -->\n            <rect x=\"240\" y=\"320\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"290\" y=\"345\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"290\" y=\"365\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Down arrow 3 -->\n            <path d=\"M 290 400 L 290 420\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Level 4 -->\n            <rect x=\"240\" y=\"420\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"290\" y=\"445\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"290\" y=\"465\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">512</text>\n            \n            <!-- Down arrow 4 -->\n            <path d=\"M 290 500 L 290 520\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Bottom (Level 5) -->\n            <rect x=\"240\" y=\"520\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"290\" y=\"545\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"290\" y=\"565\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1024</text>\n            \n            <!-- Expanding Path (Decoder) -->\n            <!-- Up arrow 1 -->\n            <path d=\"M 380 550 L 400 550\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"390\" y=\"540\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" text-anchor=\"middle\">up-conv</text>\n            \n            <!-- Level 4 decoder -->\n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"420\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"445\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"465\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">512</text>\n            \n            <!-- Up arrow 2 -->\n            <path d=\"M 470 400 L 470 380\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Level 3 decoder -->\n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"320\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"345\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"365\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Up arrow 3 -->\n            <path d=\"M 470 300 L 470 280\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Level 2 decoder -->\n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"220\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"245\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"265\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">128</text>\n            \n            <!-- Up arrow 4 -->\n            <path d=\"M 470 200 L 470 180\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Level 1 decoder -->\n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"120\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"145\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"165\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">64</text>\n            \n            <!-- Final 1x1 conv -->\n            <path d=\"M 540 150 L 580 150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"560\" y=\"140\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1\u00d71 conv</text>\n            \n            <!-- Output -->\n            <rect x=\"600\" y=\"120\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"660\" y=\"140\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Segmentation</text>\n            <text x=\"660\" y=\"160\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Map</text>\n            \n            <!-- Skip connections (dashed lines) -->\n            <!-- Skip 1 -->\n            <path d=\"M 340 150 L 420 150\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"10,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n            <text x=\"380\" y=\"140\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#f39c12\" text-anchor=\"middle\">copy & crop</text>\n            \n            <!-- Skip 2 -->\n            <path d=\"M 340 250 L 420 250\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"10,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Skip 3 -->\n            <path d=\"M 340 350 L 420 350\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"10,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Skip 4 -->\n            <path d=\"M 340 450 L 420 450\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"10,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Legend -->\n            <g transform=\"translate(800, 150)\">\n                <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"0.95\"/>\n                <text x=\"150\" y=\"30\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Legend</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"20\" y=\"50\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#e74c3c\"/>\n                <text x=\"90\" y=\"67\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Encoder (Contracting)</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"20\" y=\"85\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#27ae60\"/>\n                <text x=\"90\" y=\"102\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Decoder (Expanding)</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"20\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#9b59b6\"/>\n                <text x=\"90\" y=\"137\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Bottleneck</text>\n                \n                <path d=\"M 20 155 L 80 155\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\"/>\n                <text x=\"90\" y=\"160\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Skip Connections</text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow markers -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead-orange\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#f39c12\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Additional architectural details -->\n            <g transform=\"translate(1200, 300)\">\n                <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"0.95\"/>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"30\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Architecture Details</text>\n                \n                <text x=\"20\" y=\"60\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Each conv block: 3\u00d73 conv \u2192 ReLU \u2192 3\u00d73 conv \u2192 ReLU</text>\n                <text x=\"20\" y=\"85\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Max pooling: 2\u00d72 with stride 2</text>\n                <text x=\"20\" y=\"110\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Up-convolution: 2\u00d72 with stride 2</text>\n                <text x=\"20\" y=\"135\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Skip connections preserve spatial information</text>\n                <text x=\"20\" y=\"160\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Copy & crop: match decoder feature map size</text>\n                <text x=\"20\" y=\"185\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Final layer: 1\u00d71 conv for class prediction</text>\n                <text x=\"20\" y=\"210\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Symmetric U-shaped architecture</text>\n                <text x=\"20\" y=\"235\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Enables precise localization + context</text>\n                <text x=\"20\" y=\"260\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Effective for biomedical image segmentation</text>\n            </g>\n            \n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>U-Net Architecture</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        \n        h1 {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin: 0 0 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>U-Net (Ronneberger et al., 2015)</h1>\n        \n        <svg width=\"1840\" height=\"900\" viewBox=\"0 0 1840 900\">\n            <!-- Background -->\n            <rect width=\"1840\" height=\"900\" fill=\"none\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Resolution labels on the left -->\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"150\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\" text-anchor=\"middle\">572\u00d7572</text>\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"250\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\" text-anchor=\"middle\">284\u00d7284</text>\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"350\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\" text-anchor=\"middle\">142\u00d7142</text>\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"450\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\" text-anchor=\"middle\">71\u00d771</text>\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"550\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\" text-anchor=\"middle\">35\u00d735</text>\n            \n            <!-- Input -->\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"120\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"140\" y=\"145\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Input</text>\n            <text x=\"140\" y=\"165\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Image</text>\n            \n            <!-- Contracting Path (Encoder) -->\n            <!-- Level 1 -->\n            <rect x=\"250\" y=\"120\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"155\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">64</text>\n            \n            <!-- Down arrow 1 -->\n            <path d=\"M 300 190 L 300 210\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"205\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">2\u00d72 max pool</text>\n            \n            <!-- Level 2 -->\n            <rect x=\"250\" y=\"220\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#e67e22\" stroke=\"#d35400\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"255\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">128</text>\n            \n            <!-- Down arrow 2 -->\n            <path d=\"M 300 290 L 300 310\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"305\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">2\u00d72 max pool</text>\n            \n            <!-- Level 3 -->\n            <rect x=\"250\" y=\"320\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"355\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Down arrow 3 -->\n            <path d=\"M 300 390 L 300 410\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"405\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">2\u00d72 max pool</text>\n            \n            <!-- Level 4 -->\n            <rect x=\"250\" y=\"420\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"455\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">512</text>\n            \n            <!-- Down arrow 4 -->\n            <path d=\"M 300 490 L 300 510\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"505\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">2\u00d72 max pool</text>\n            \n            <!-- Bottom (Level 5) -->\n            <rect x=\"250\" y=\"520\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"#7d3c98\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"555\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1024</text>\n            \n            <!-- Expanding Path (Decoder) -->\n            <!-- Up arrow 1 -->\n            <path d=\"M 400 550 L 420 550\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"430\" y=\"545\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">up-conv 2\u00d72</text>\n            \n            <!-- Level 4 decoder -->\n            <rect x=\"550\" y=\"420\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"600\" y=\"455\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">512</text>\n            \n            <!-- Up arrow 2 -->\n            <path d=\"M 600 410 L 600 390\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"620\" y=\"405\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">up-conv 2\u00d72</text>\n            \n            <!-- Level 3 decoder -->\n            <rect x=\"550\" y=\"320\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"600\" y=\"355\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Up arrow 3 -->\n            <path d=\"M 600 310 L 600 290\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"620\" y=\"305\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">up-conv 2\u00d72</text>\n            \n            <!-- Level 2 decoder -->\n            <rect x=\"550\" y=\"220\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#e67e22\" stroke=\"#d35400\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"600\" y=\"255\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">128</text>\n            \n            <!-- Up arrow 4 -->\n            <path d=\"M 600 210 L 600 190\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"620\" y=\"205\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">up-conv 2\u00d72</text>\n            \n            <!-- Level 1 decoder -->\n            <rect x=\"550\" y=\"120\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"600\" y=\"155\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">64</text>\n            \n            <!-- Skip connections (dashed lines) -->\n            <path d=\"M 350 150 L 550 150\" stroke=\"#95a5a6\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\" fill=\"none\"/>\n            <text x=\"450\" y=\"140\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" text-anchor=\"middle\">copy and crop</text>\n            \n            <path d=\"M 350 250 L 550 250\" stroke=\"#95a5a6\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\" fill=\"none\"/>\n            <text x=\"450\" y=\"240\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" text-anchor=\"middle\">copy and crop</text>\n            \n            <path d=\"M 350 350 L 550 350\" stroke=\"#95a5a6\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\" fill=\"none\"/>\n            <text x=\"450\" y=\"340\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" text-anchor=\"middle\">copy and crop</text>\n            \n            <path d=\"M 350 450 L 550 450\" stroke=\"#95a5a6\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\" fill=\"none\"/>\n            <text x=\"450\" y=\"440\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" text-anchor=\"middle\">copy and crop</text>\n            \n            <!-- Final 1x1 conv -->\n            <path d=\"M 650 150 L 720 150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"685\" y=\"140\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1\u00d71 conv</text>\n            \n            <!-- Output -->\n            <rect x=\"750\" y=\"120\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"145\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Output</text>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"165\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Segmentation</text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend -->\n            <g transform=\"translate(950, 150)\">\n                <text x=\"0\" y=\"0\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Legend</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"0\" y=\"30\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#e74c3c\"/>\n                <text x=\"40\" y=\"45\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Double Conv Block</text>\n                \n                <path d=\"M 0 70 L 30 70\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                <text x=\"40\" y=\"75\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Down/Up sampling</text>\n                \n                <path d=\"M 0 100 L 30 100\" stroke=\"#95a5a6\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"6,3\"/>\n                <text x=\"40\" y=\"105\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Skip connection</text>\n                \n                <text x=\"0\" y=\"140\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Architecture Details:</text>\n                <text x=\"0\" y=\"165\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Each block: 3\u00d73 conv \u2192 ReLU \u2192 3\u00d73 conv \u2192 ReLU</text>\n                <text x=\"0\" y=\"185\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Contracting: 2\u00d72 max pooling (stride 2)</text>\n                <text x=\"0\" y=\"205\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Expanding: 2\u00d72 up-convolution</text>\n                <text x=\"0\" y=\"225\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Skip connections preserve fine details</text>\n                <text x=\"0\" y=\"245\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2022 Final layer: 1\u00d71 conv for classification</text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow marker definition -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" \n                        refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Input arrow -->\n            <path d=\"M 200 150 L 240 150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Connection from bottom to decoder -->\n            <path d=\"M 350 550 L 400 550\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 500 550 L 500 480 L 550 480\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}